## Architecture

### Folder Structure
```
app/                    # Expo Router — file-based routes (web + native)
  (auth)/
    login.tsx
  (app)/
    [checklistId]/
      index.tsx         # task list
      tasks/[taskId].tsx  # task detail
  _layout.tsx
src/
  api/                  # axios client, endpoint wrappers, shared types
  auth/                 # token store (web: localStorage / native: SecureStore), useAuth Zustand store
  features/
    checklists/         # checklist switcher, hooks
    tasks/
      list/             # TaskListView, VirtualTaskList (web) / FlashList (native), TaskRow, TaskTree, MindMapView, OutlineView
      detail/           # TaskDetailView, SubTaskTree, MarkdownRenderer
      shared/           # QuickDatePicker, PriorityPicker, ContextMenu, CreateTaskInput
  components/           # BottomSheet, Toast, Spinner, TaskSkeleton, InlineMarkdown
  lib/                  # taskTree, dateSort, dateUtils, taskCache (IndexedDB on web / AsyncStorage on native)
  platform/             # thin platform-specific shims (storage, haptics, share, etc.)
```

### Platform Shims (`src/platform/`)
Abstract every platform-divergent API behind a shim so feature code stays portable:

| Shim | Web | Native |
|------|-----|--------|
| `storage.ts` | `localStorage` / IndexedDB | `expo-secure-store` / `AsyncStorage` |
| `haptics.ts` | no-op | `expo-haptics` |
| `share.ts` | Web Share API | `expo-sharing` |
| `listContainer.tsx` | `@tanstack/react-virtual` wrapper | `FlashList` wrapper |

