## Task Detail View
Route: `/(app)/[checklistId]/tasks/[taskId]`

- **Header**: back arrow / close, editable task title (inline, saves on blur), status pill, due-date pill (opens quick date picker), priority badge (opens picker), ancestor breadcrumb.
- **Body**: task `details` rendered as full block Markdown (DOMPurify-sanitized on web; a safe Markdown renderer on native).
- **Sub-tasks section**: full descendant subtree with checkbox, content (inline Markdown), priority, due date. Inline "**+ Add sub-task**" input at the bottom.
- **Footer**: created/updated timestamps (muted).

