## Offline & Caching
- **Web**: IndexedDB (via `src/lib/db.ts`) caches tasks and checklists. Object stores: `tasks`, `lists`, `list_states`, `users`, `temp_objects`, `files_storage`.
- **Native**: `AsyncStorage` (or SQLite via `expo-sqlite`) mirrors the same data model.
- On load, serve cached data instantly while the network fetch completes in the background (stale-while-revalidate).
- `taskCache.ts` exposes `getCachedTasks`, `cacheTasks`, `getCachedLists`, `cacheLists` — implementations differ by platform shim.

