## Responsive & Mobile / Native Requirements
- Touch targets ≥ 44×44 dp on all platforms.
- Safe-area insets: `env(safe-area-inset-*)` on web; `useSafeAreaInsets` (react-native-safe-area-context) on native.
- No hover-only interactions — long-press replaces right-click on touch.
- Keyboard handling on iOS: `font-size: 16px` on inputs (prevents Safari zoom).
- Native status bar managed via `expo-status-bar`.
- Haptic feedback (via `expo-haptics`) on task completion and long-press, on native only.

